## Notation

```
[path/to/file.ext]
  fn function_name(param_type param, ...) -> return_type
    calls: fn1, fn2, fn3
    called_by: fn4, fn5
  struct StructName { field1: type, field2: type }
  enum EnumName { VAL1, VAL2, VAL3 }
  macro MACRO_NAME(args)
  global variable_name: type
```

- `calls:` lists functions this function directly invokes
- `called_by:` lists functions that directly invoke this function
- Only PUBLIC / EXPORTED symbols are listed unless internal symbols cross file boundaries
- Call graph edges are best-effort — static analysis only

