    cache_write --> bdev_write
    cache_write --> dlm_lock
```

To regenerate the call graph:
```bash
python3 ~/.claude/skills/project-awareness/scripts/generate_mermaid_callgraph.py \
    .claude/awareness/structural-map.md --cross-subsystem-only
```

For a subsystem-filtered view:
```bash
python3 ~/.claude/skills/project-awareness/scripts/generate_mermaid_callgraph.py \
    .claude/awareness/structural-map.md --subsystem {subsystem_name}
```

For a subsystem-level summary:
```bash
python3 ~/.claude/skills/project-awareness/scripts/generate_mermaid_callgraph.py \
    .claude/awareness/structural-map.md --summary
```
